00:25:58,650 --> 00:26:00,000
So we're okay now?

485
00:26:00,010 --> 00:26:02,810
Yes. Yes, we're great.

486
00:26:04,810 --> 00:26:05,960
David, please don't be a stranger.

487
00:26:05,970 --> 00:26:10,380
