00:40:48,830 --> 00:40:52,310
"Each one is so lucky to have gotten your kind heart."

737
00:40:52,750 --> 00:40:57,830
"And no matter what mistakes I've made or to the extent of the pain those mistakes may have caused,"

738
00:40:57,840 --> 00:41:01,480
"I know I've done at least one right thing in this life..."

739
00:41:01,960 --> 00:41:05,780
"and that was to fall in love and make a family with you."

740
00:41:09,100 --> 00:41:10,400
Thank you.

741
00:41:14,970 --> 00:41:16,310
Thank you.

742
00:41:18,850 --> 00:41:21,400
Thank you all so much for being here.

743
00:41:21,410 --> 00:41:23,320
It means so much to me...

744
00:41:24,250 --> 00:41:26,390
especially after these past few months.

745
00:41:26,400 --> 00:41:28,730
We have all been through so much.

746
00:41:28,740 --> 00:41:33,180
And I'm--I'm so grateful to all of you.

747
00:41:34,220 --> 00:41:36,480
Cheers.

748
00:41:37,480 --> 00:41:39,100
Happy Thanksgiving, everyone!

749
00:41:39,110 --> 00:41:41,820
Happy Thanksgiving!

750
00:41:42,760 --> 00:41:44,200
Cheers.

751
00:41:44,240 --> 00:41:45,690
Go ahead.

752
00:41:46,600 --> 00:41:47,660
It's the right time.

753
00:41:47,670 --> 00:41:50,070
Wait, wait, "right time" for what?

754
00:41:53,260 --> 00:41:54,790
We're having a baby.

755
00:41:57,050 --> 00:42:02,540
"Because our family means so much more to me than my mistakes suggest."

756
00:42:02,570 --> 00:42:08,080
"Our family is everything, the best thing I ever did in my entire life."

757
00:42:08,670 --> 00:42:12,030
"With love and remorse, William."

